Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's work?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything going okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Rosemary?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's made lots of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be getting used to school by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get going now, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you a picture of Rosemary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you let me see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about here, two days from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've stopped drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life has gone back to normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... this might be the first time I've  \N actually lived a normal life...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I understand the significance of what I've lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let her decide if she wants to see you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I have to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another coffee, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.98,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(128,0)\pos(359,339)}Article of Evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, what kind of man do you think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Richard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think you are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are here to receive my counseling, that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you, I'm not a fortune teller!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:04:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just years of experience dealing with clients, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who is the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man was the one who found Fahren's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But supposedly he was just a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Richard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard work is good, but you also need  \N some time to relax, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking my time with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... might get to see my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be excited, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you do see her, you won't be  \N able to get back what you've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, never touch alcohol again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are going back to work now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's about time you faced the  \N case that got you kicked off the police force?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was seventeen years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A serial killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shot... and killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I got drunk while on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to run away from that, even if you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't erase the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is important...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is to get past that incident.  Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a very good student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I get a 100%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give out full points that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, people who score a 100% are boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karl Neumann...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A student majoring in economics  \N at that University of Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Fahren...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he told the prostitute that he's Schuwald's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not this is true has yet to be proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this boy knows something about the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Richard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finished cleaning, so I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's no trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy for a guy to keep his place this clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:08:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.  It's been much worse than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a new picture of your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to see her soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!  I'm so happy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your daughter will be delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any daughter would be happy to see her parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:25.10,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(237,0)\pos(355,359)}University of Munich \N - Friedrich Emmanuel School -
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, were you able to hand in your report?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karl Neumann...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you tell Schuwald that you are his son?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a fraud too, or are you the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really are Schuwald's son...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A father always wants to see his child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said... she doesn't want to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.  Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to order something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... A whiskey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go to Dad's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you are older...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still want to meet him after you've grown up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you mustn't want anything from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't hate him, even if he acts cold towards you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't hate him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father meant to give you this when you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"With none to love it..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...Lares' daffodil bloomed with pride."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"With none of heart..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...Pieria's trees rustled."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"O!  You furrows of blood that trail the  \N footsteps of nameless humans."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Neumann, you really have \N become a wonderful reader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's noteworthy that your Latin has improved  \N so much in this short period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, someone's been tutoring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be an excellent teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just his Latin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just in law and economics...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he has a perfect philosophy about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so perfect, he's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me, Mr. Schuwald...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a guy like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if he were you real son...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He smiled...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schuwald smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he thinks you are fit to be his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I was jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's clear that you are better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate myself for being jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Schuwald that you are his real son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I never intended to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did tell him, he wouldn't believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even worse, he'd just see me as one  \N of those hyenas after his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know what kind of life my  \N mother led before passing away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know the feelings \N that have driven me this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to know the truth before  \N he thinks of me that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you are going to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are going to make him understand the whole truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't believe a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a way to make him believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:15:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that will make him  \N believe you are his real son...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't have anything like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't have anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intentions of telling him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you making me teach you Latin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you want him to be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you want him to like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of quitting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my part time reading job...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for worrying about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... okay now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I do have some proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no intention of claiming to be his real  \N son by shoving something like that in his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My foster parents are coming to see me next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... so you don't change your mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...maybe I should hold onto that  \N article of evidence for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you are doing okay.  Right, mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried if you were still eating properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've been watching what I eat because  \N I'd get fat if I ate out all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mom's cooking would make you fat, also.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it tastes so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's college going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you made any friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, someone I can talk to about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  Those are the best kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:17:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell everything is going great  \N just by looking at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really grateful that I can study like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you getting so formal all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been passed around by so many  \N foster parents all this time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you two have been really nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are a wonderful child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Mr. and Mrs. Lindner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you ever stop calling us that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to become our adopted son yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked us to give you some time  \N after starting college, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe in you .
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe in us as well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:18:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your real mother and father may \N still be alive somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what we do, we may never  \N become your real parents, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the two of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are my real mother and father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to order the special wine today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you bring us the wine menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's a special day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Mr. Neumann?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Schuwald...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about you quitting your part time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being so selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well to improve your Latin so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really going to miss you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...reading something to me one last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'd be happy to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will chapter three of "From Aoelis to Limnos" be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That deep sea of mystery..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...was it not wishing death even upon God Phoebus?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What pleasure did it have..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...other than to bring death to sons  \N and daughters like Cerberus?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Now, move on, Zeus murmured."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Move on.  Move on."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dance in the shadowy temples of the gods."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, gods of Juno, dweller of the land, the sea..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...and the heavens."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"From the summit of the Parthenon..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Take... the forbidden apple... of Campania..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...and bring all here..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...to save my heart..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My heart..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Schuwald...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That call was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the most heartfelt recitation I have ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you keep this from me all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is indeed the rabbit's foot I  \N gave to your mother, Margot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good luck charm to bring you fortune from birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made you suffer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.44,0:22:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who told me everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to be working as my secretary from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a boy I can trust.
